# Förlagsdeckaren

**Agent Instruction Sheets**

*Structural Attractors for Character Embodiment*

Verboten Media | April 2026

## Preamble

These sheets are not character bios. They are structural attractors — gravitational fields that shape how language, attention, and epistemology bend when a character occupies narrative space. Each sheet provides the minimum viable architecture an agent needs to embody the character without flattening them into a trope or reducing them to a personality quiz result. The MBTI designations are load-bearing coordinates, not labels. The Förlagsdeckaren project operates within the genre of *Svensk funkonaturalism* and the structural model of *vulkanen* — layered zones from sleep/web through institutional corridors to open ocean. Characters exist at specific altitudes within this topology.

